                                                                                                Sustainment                                            
                                            
Supply Chain Management (SCM)
VSE's solutions address every aspect of supply chain management processes to manage and optimize the many facets of the supply chain, from our managed inventory program to transportation and logistics. More
Maintenance, Repair, and Overhaul (MRO)
VSE is one of the nation's leading providers of maintenance, reset, overhaul and modernization support, ensuring land, sea and air systems are capable of performing their operational missions throughout their lifecycle. More

Engineering Services

                                                                                                VSE provides comprehensive engineering services that span applied research, concept generation, initial design, and the upgrading and modification of system hardware and software. More.
                                                                                            
Training
VSE's training personnel have developed and integrated training and training support programs that include management sciences, industrial/trade crafts, new equipment training, operator training, and maintenance training programs. More
IT, Energy, and Management Consulting

IT Solutions

VSE provides client-focused IT services and state-of-the-art products spanning all phases of the system life cycle and an array of platforms and applications. More
Energy & Management Consulting
With services spanning project management, strategic program planning, energy conservation, policy analysis and regulatory compliance, VSE's consulting expertise focuses on practical applications to achieve an ideal balance between effectiveness and efficiency. More































 









